  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>When you add <code>'s</code> after a noun, it shows that something belongs to or is connected to that noun. It's like adding a label to say that this thing belongs to this person or object. <code>'s</code> indicates the ownership or possession.</p>\n<p>Examples: <code>This is Tom's camera.</code> (this camera belongs to Tom). <code>That's today's newspaper.</code> (that newspaper has the news for today).</p>\n</section>",
